            , who lives in Portland-place. My livery coat is kept in the carriage, which stood in <placeName id="t18240218-79-crimeloc446">Beaufort Mews</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18240218-79-crimeloc446" type="placeName" value="Beaufort Mews"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18240218-79-crimeloc446" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240218-79-off443 t18240218-79-crimeloc446"></join>. On a Friday about the 21st of November, I went into the Mews, about half-past six o'clock in the evening, and missed it. The prisoner was occasionally employed about the Mews; it was safe at one o'clock.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240218-79-person830">
                  ISAAC 
                  LAZARUS
               <interp inst="t18240218-79-person830" type="surname" value="LAZARUS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240218-79-person830" type="given" value="ISAAC"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240218-79-person830" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was calling</p>
               <p>"Old Clothes" in Arlington-street, on Monday, the 23d or 24th of November, and saw the prisoner standing outside the Blue Posts, public house; he called me into the house, and offered me a box coat; I bought it of him for 2 l., and spent 2 s. I sold it to Simmons, of Newington.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240218-79-person831">
                  THOMAS 
                  YOUNG
               <interp inst="t18240218-79-person831" type="surname" value="YOUNG"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240218-79-person831" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240218-79-person831" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I keep a coffee-shop in Woodstock-street; I saw the prisoner following Lazarus with the coat - he borrowed 11 s. of me to pay him for it.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182402180044"></xptr>
            
